{"tid":254775,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"首都廣場舖下周開價55萬翻叮　恐要蝕87.2% (19:42)","createTime":"2017-05-23T12:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T15:55:04.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9012bae9d1efd2c91165c578ddc7053c02bb332","tid":254775,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T12:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170523/img/20170523194235fi_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170523%2Fimg%2F20170523194235fi_p1.jpg&h=c9bab8e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=CUR0kzXGIm1HC%2F%2BZBX5zt5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=2922a046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】尖沙咀首都廣場舖位劈價拍賣，今日透過環亞物業拍賣公開拍賣的首都廣場2樓單號舖，開價75萬港元，舖位最終未能售出。據環亞物業拍賣資料，該實用面積44方呎的首都廣場舖位，開價即時勁劈20萬元或26.7%，以55萬元開價於下周三再度推出。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，業主於2013年8月以431.2萬元買入上述舖位。若以開價55萬元售出，業主將勁蝕376.2萬元，蝕幅將高達87.2%，有機會成為該拆場蝕幅最大個案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170523/20170523194235fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170523%2F20170523194235fi.html&d=CUR0kzXGIm1HC%2F%2BZBX5zt5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=ac7fbc28\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170523/20170523194235fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"64daaf6bc686fc7786ae65f88e2170340303ed37","tid":254775,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:11:57.000Z","msg":"擺張床入去訓得唔得？即刻升價十倍"},{"pid":"89bfb8dd94745ed71bc0209c4397df9af54f0708","tid":254775,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:14:53.000Z","msg":"44呎都55萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424db5ab2862756a4f9a2497306bff05a4bc9060","tid":254775,"uid":76078,"lik